title: Tamiri Bites
description: Edmonton's first 100% raw/vegan unbakery. Gluten-free, soy-free and refined sugar free. Menu includes many flavors of cakes plus brownies, energy bites, chocolates, cookies, and seasonal specials. Sells prepackaged raw vegan products. Has an online store, sells at farmer's markets and in retail locations. Open by appointment only on weekdays.
